  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094122/summer-suprising-838x330.jpg?width=208&amp;height=21" alt="Surprising walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/1a836c64373d46f781c8e53a5eeb571a" /></p>
<p>Join us on a walking holiday and discover the unexpected. Whether you are looking to escape the crowds and relax in a spa, or discover historic towns, charming villages and hidden waterfalls, our walking holidays offer a refreshing break that will delight and surprise you.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2>Surprising walking destinations</h2>
<p>Discover the surprising side of <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760}" title="Austria">Austria</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France">France</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049}" title="Slovenia">Slovenia</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a> at these top summer resorts.</p>
<div class="g6">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora, Slovenia</a></h2>
<p><img style="width: 407px; height: 243px;" src="/media/13094104/kranjska-gora-slovenia.jpg?width=407&amp;height=243&amp;mode=max" alt="slovenia holidays" data-udi="umb://media/e81d9f2f319c4104b1de22973be6bd14" /></p>
<p><strong>Best for</strong> mountain views, easy, moderate and challenging walks</p>
<p><strong>What our experts say...</strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">This is an amazing destination for an active holiday in nature, surrounded by Slovenia’s highest peaks in the Julian Alps. Discover the most beautiful corners of the Upper Sava valley, with legends and fairy tales of its mystical past.</p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/51984d8419bc459f98223009757f4ed0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/51984d8419bc459f98223009757f4ed0}" title="Murren">Murren, Switzerland</a></h2>
<p><img style="width: 407px; height: 245px;" src="/media/13096142/murren-switzerland-1.png?width=407&amp;height=245&amp;mode=max" alt="Murren holidays" data-udi="umb://media/9b99a23a705f441cbea32a47ee0818ca" /></p>
<p><strong>Best for</strong> mountain and glacier views, village tradition, moderate and challenging walks</p>
<p><strong>What our experts say....</strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">The village of Mürren, at the top of the Lauterbrunnen Valley, is full of surprises and hidden gems. Guests can test their head for heights on the thrill walk at Birg and enjoy a prosecco brunch at Schilthorn's revolving restaurant with amazing views over the Bernese Alps.</p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9}" title="Lake Iseo">Lake Iseo, Italy</a></h2>
<p><img style="width: 409px; height: 246px;" src="/media/13094108/lake-iseo-italy.jpg?width=409&amp;height=246&amp;mode=max" alt="lake iseo holidays" data-udi="umb://media/864414b9ec264e98bbccff5a1755f636" /></p>
<p><strong>Best for</strong> family hiking, difficult hiking, lake views, intimate lakeside towns, wine lovers</p>
<p><strong>What our experts say...</strong></p>
<p>Home to the famous <a rel="noopener" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Franciacorta_DOCG" target="_blank">Franciacorta DOCG Sparkling wine</a>, this is the best place to come if you want  to do some stunning lake view walking, stopping at vineyards along the way.  Make sure you check out Monte Isola which is the largest inhabited lake island in Europe.</p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc}" title="Morzine">Morzine, France</a></h2>
<p><img style="width: 420px; height: 253px;" src="/media/13094109/morzine-france.jpg?width=420&amp;height=253&amp;mode=max" alt="Morzine holidays" data-udi="umb://media/404b22954347404aa5dd51ede40e2a75" /></p>
<p><strong>Best for</strong> cycling, lake &amp; mountain views, animal spotting and easy, moderate &amp; challenging walks</p>
<p><strong>What our experts say...</strong></p>
<p>Originally a mining and farming town, Morzine is a lively and surprisingly historic little town. Head to the next door town Les Lindarets and check out the hundreds of goats that casually roam around the streets. Morzine is always ringing with the sound of church bells and there are no high rise buildings, so you get a really quintessential alpine town feel.</p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Discover hotels with the unexpected</h2>
<p>At these incredible hotels, you'll be treated to more than just stylish decor. You'll find plenty of surprising extras, from unique dining experiences to incredible spas.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/2eca36efaf4346c4b82f4e67499fc58a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2eca36efaf4346c4b82f4e67499fc58a}" title="Hotel Alpbacherhof" data-anchor="#">Hotel Alpbacherhof, Austria</a></strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 290px; height: 138px;" src="/media/13094110/alpbacherhof-2014-06-06_0799-1.jpg?width=290&amp;height=138&amp;mode=max" alt="Hotel Alpbacherhof" data-udi="umb://media/6b79f5146074426d92fe26d001db4443" /></p>
<p>One of Alpbach’s leading hotels, we love their interconnected indoor / outdoor pool and garden relaxation area - perfect after a day of walking the trails. </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/83040257fea44fbea7942a48629cc9cb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/83040257fea44fbea7942a48629cc9cb}" title="Hotel Alpina">Alpina Eclectic Hotel, France</a></strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 284px; height: 135px;" src="/media/13086019/alpina-balcon-1_4.jpg?width=284&amp;height=135&amp;mode=max" alt="Hotel Alpina" data-udi="umb://media/1612aa4584734aae87f40fead3c5171f" /></p>
<p>This hotel offers impressive mountain views with a cosy atmosphere. Their Vista bar and restaurant offers stunning 180° panoramic views of Chamonix and Mont Blanc.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/aed5ab65747f4034a4453aa23eefc6da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/aed5ab65747f4034a4453aa23eefc6da}" title="Hotel Post">Hotel Post, Austria</a></strong></p>
<p><img src="/media/13099167/hotel-post-ischgl-aussenpool-1-1.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/ebf8833251d245d3833d8b04537bc9e9" /></p>
<p>Hotel Post is equipped with everything you need for a great stay; from the Sauna Master and daily guided sauna infusion, to the gym and yoga classes.</p>
<p> </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/29edcd3c50e4458281799c0617b52ba5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/29edcd3c50e4458281799c0617b52ba5}" title="Hotel La Folie Douce">Hotel La Folie Douce, France</a></strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 282px; height: 151px;" src="/media/13082623/la-folie-douce-hotel-chamonix-piscine.jpg?width=282&amp;height=151&amp;mode=max" alt="How La Folie Douce" data-udi="umb://media/bb1e58750b0249c6a0a8be109dc63620" /></p>
<p>Relax at La Folie Douce and enjoy the magnificent Alpine scenery. The hotel has a large spa with sauna, relaxation room, sun terrace and steam room, plus an outdoor pool with fantastic views of Mont Blanc.</p>
<p> </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/1c5894c85da24d24938effa0e8112f37" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1c5894c85da24d24938effa0e8112f37}" title="Hotel Bohinj"><strong>Hotel Bohinj, Slovenia</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 288px; height: 154px;" src="/media/13089329/hotel_bohinj_exterior_day_three.jpg?width=288&amp;height=154&amp;mode=max" alt="Hotel Bohinj" data-udi="umb://media/bbf4ac4ac6174dd58d076d7cd74cea77" /></p>
<p>You’ll have everything you need for a great stay at this hotel. On-site spa facilities make it the ideal location for a romantic getaway or relaxing break, with treatments such as Finnish and Turkish saunas, an ice fountain, massage pool and salt room.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/518cc472770341548f0da194220efeeb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/518cc472770341548f0da194220efeeb}" title="Romantik Hotel Schweizerhof"><strong>Romantik Hotel Schweizerhof, Switzerland</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 293px; height: 157px;" src="/media/13096028/romantik-hotel.jpg?width=293&amp;height=157" alt="Romantik Hotel" data-udi="umb://media/b0c61c55a56f4f5fa1b8082af7e89053" /></p>
<p>Experience the perfect blend of Swiss hospitality and modern comforts at the Hotel Schweizerhof. This country-house hotel is beautifully-furnished in an attractive Alpine style and has charming gardens, with bush–covered verandas, lounging areas, and an indoor swimming pool.</p>
</div>
<div>  </div>
<div>
<p> </p>
</div>
<div style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/c9869bf0e4e9431d98d0277c1db49284" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9869bf0e4e9431d98d0277c1db49284}" title="Deals" class="c-btn"></a></div>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2146c02aa3364cbeb1c0ef9561bc4426" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2146c02aa3364cbeb1c0ef9561bc4426}" title="Next Summer" class="c-btn">View 2025 holiday Deals</a></p>
</div>
